title: Good Directions 954P Smithsonian Arrow Weathervane - Polished Copper
description: Whichever the way the wind blows, this decorative arrow, a typical design from the 1800s, will grace the rooftop of your house, barn, garage, or cupola. Our Good Directions' artisans use Old World techniques to handcraft this fully functional, standard-size weathervane that's unsurpassed in style, quality and durability, and carries the logo of the highly prestigious Smithsonian® Collection! A great gift for folk art enthusiasts!
